desc: Biofilam is the purest, all-natural brown seaweed extract supplement made from Laminaria Japonica. Detoxifies body. Contains Fucoidan. The original Modifilan.

layout.text: BIOFILAM® is classified as an “Adsorbent” of antitoxic materials. It may prevent toxic pollutants from absorbing into the body while the body is exposed to radiation or other toxic pollutants.
